Today is the perfect day for a ✨mindset reset✨ and to grow our 🍑! The #1 request I get is for affordable fitness reccs for small spaces so I’m kicking off with my current fave: The Booty Sprout! 

This is a lightweight, portable lower body machine that targets the glutes and is great for ALL fitness levels. It has been a game changer in my glute game and as you can see it’s a bit of a butt kicker 😏🍊 

Head to the link in my stories and use code TAYA10 to save and start growing that Booty bestieeee 👏 #bootysprout #bootygainz #fitnessforall #plussizefitness #plussizefitnessjourney #plussizefitnessmotivation #boporevolution

node.text:
Happy ✨Mindset Reset Monday✨ bestie! Today I woke up with an overwhelming sense of gratitude, faith, and hope. It seems as if everything in my life is falling into place; I am on a clear path to fulfilling my dreams of becoming a doctor, my business is thriving, and I’m creating a sanctuary within my home. 

I don’t discuss my faith much on socials because I understand that it doesn’t resonate with everyone. But what I will say is I am a firm believer in meeting God halfway. He can put you on the path but ultimately it’s up to us to utilize the gifts he’s given us. Your gifts can touch the world, even if you don’t believe it. I’ve spent the last year digging DEEP to heal. I’ve healed my mindset, self-limiting beliefs, and my home. I’ve worked my butt off in school and have spent the last year building my business. It’s been a long journey, but it’s finally starting to pay off. 

On stories we’re discussing what we’re grateful for today. Head to stories to join the convo, or sound off in the comments below ⬇️ Conquer the week, bestie! #mindsetreset #mindsetresetmonday #productivityhabits #medstudent

node.text:
💀😭Alas, I’d like to introduce you to the first part of my new, highly curated BLOOPERS series! This is hands down some of my best work yet and I’m delighted to share it with you. 😭💀

Why, you ask, am I putting my absolute worst most “unflattering” photos on the internet for 1.7M+ people to see? Because I think every woman needs a reminder that social media is a highlight reel, and even your favorite creators don’t look like your favorite creators. What you see on our feeds is THE photo. Sometimes it’s THE photo out of 75. I’m not kidding. There have been times when I have sifted through nearly 100 photos to find “the ONE.” And even after being on social media for a few years now, I STILLLL get down on myself about this.

So, with that, I’ll leave you with my double chin, fupa, and imperfect skin as an example of being HUMAN. Much love to you girlies 🧡 #bloopers #bopo #instagramvsreality #instagramvsreallife
